objects.description:
The application allows you to create and store lists in a convenient way. On the cover, you can navigate through the generated lists and complete the tasks.

Main features:
- Intuitive interface;
- Cover navigation;
- Intellectual tasks adding;
- Copy/paste tasks between lists;
- Dropbox synchronization;
- Sorting modes;
- Favorite lists;
- Statistic and filters.

